Dialogs.Dialog: What a coincidence. Are you taking a walk？
I think meeting you like this is kind of wonderful.
...Teehee. So, we think alike, eh？ I'm glad.
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. Are you taking a walk today too？
Ah, I'm so sorry. I'm just surprised...
It felt like I would be able to see you, so I came here. And here we are.
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲... Haha. We meet again.
This kind of thing makes me feel like the bond between us is quite strong.
Hehe. Isn't it？ Are you going to watch the movie？
Is that so？ What a pity...
That means you have already watched it right, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Yes. We should have come to watch it together in the first place, right？
Ah, the next screening is about to start. Then I'll walk you to the entrance.
By the way, are you by yourself？
Hehe. All right then. Enjoy yourself.
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. We really meet often.
When it comes to this, don't you think we have some kind of inseparable fate？
...Hey, don't answer it so bluntly. It's embarrassing...
Well, yeah... How about you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
I'm just about to go home.
But, since you're here, maybe I'll stay around a bit longer.
Really？ I think I should have come here earlier, then.
Hehe！ We feel the same, don't we？
Ah. There's a cute trainer there. Don't look at her too much, okay？
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲... Don't tell me this is another coincidence.
It seems so. Hey, are you doing this on purpose？
Hehe！ I don't know if the God of Coincidence is being kind to us or teasing us.
Ah, we meet by chance again...
Hehe... I think this is already fate.
We never schedule it, but we seem to run into each other every time, eh？
Well, we can't go against fate, right？
Yeah. Something like that. How about you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Me, too. But I'm about to go home.
Your face is so red. Do you have a fever？
No, I don't. I just think that it's nice that we met here, I guess...
My heart is pounding so fast for something like this. Sorry if I say something weird.
(I wonder why her words are making me feel embarrassed...)
We meet often. Are you heading home？
Yes. You just got here, but I have to go. Bad timing. Very unfortunate.
But, I'm so happy to see you. Enjoy shopping, okay？
Somehow, I felt like I might see you here today.
This is more like fate than chance, huh？ Hehe！
Yo, are you here by yourself？ Got some free time？
That sounds like a pick up line from a skirt chaser, you know？
How about having some tea with me then？
I won't. I have to run some errands.
Hehe. Don't pout. See you later, okay？
Pretty girl, wanna have some tea with me？
Ah！ Hey！ You called out to me like this again...
Hahaha！ Do you also have some errands to run today？
Yes, and I have to head home now.
Handsome man, wanna have some tea with me？
Hey, you should have told me that you were coming here.
But it also feels nice to meet each other like this, doesn't it？
Eh...？ ▲高嶺＊＊▲！？ Are you here alone...？
I never expected to see you here.
I came to exchange some coins.
Exchange coins？ Ah, they sure have plenty of coins here.
They don't allow people to exchange coins for other purposes here, right？
Yeah, I think so... Then, why are you here？
A secret. Hehe. Bye now. Enjoy your time.
(I feel like I have seen something unbelievable...)
Um, well... I guess so. Maybe？
I wonder if you're gonna tell me the truth.
▲高嶺＊＊▲！ This time, you can't run away, okay？
Hey, you're really trying hard. So cute.
D-Don't try to deceive me. Ah！
Eh？ ▲高嶺＊＊▲. What a coincidence. Are you shopping？
It's more like window shopping. How about you？
Hehe. What is that supposed to mean？
Did you find anything interesting here？
Hmm, not really... Ah, maybe next time, I should ask you for some suggestions.
Excuse me. Mama is waiting for me over there.
Is that so？ Then I'll see you later.
Hello. Are you doing nothing again today？
Today is more like I'm doing "totally nothing," I guess.
However, I'm glad to meet you here. Sort of.
Yeah, and I'm doing nothing again today...
Hehe. But, I kind of understand. You never get bored of this place.
Even so, don't just forget about me and leave me alone. As least ask me out for a date！
Oh, what a coincidence. Are you here shopping too, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Huh！ Yes, I want a CD for piano songs.
I see. Did you find it？
I see. Too bad, I have to go home now.
But, I'm glad we ran into each other. I also got a nice CD.
Hehe. I've heard this line before.
Hahaha！ Did you find any good CDs？
Well... I can't find any today. I'm going home empty-handed.
But since I met you... This wasn't a worthless trip. Hehe.
We probably can't call this a coincidence anymore.
That's what I've been thinking from the start, you know？
Ah... I'm just too slow then...
Yeah, sort of... How about you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Well, I saw a really pretty doll. However, I was really surprised when I saw its price.
And now I'm even more surprised, as I see you.
I didn't expect to see you here. Hehe. How lucky.
How about I escort you home today then？
Hehe, thanks. But, it is best if we do that some other time▼ Okay？
Do you like to come here, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Yeah, they have a lot of things. I enjoy it here.
Plus, it's even more enjoyable now that I see you here often.
We coincidentally meet like this so often.
Hehe, and that makes you happy, right？
What are you doing here ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
No, it's not bad, but... I'm wondering if you can concentrate on studying...
It's not that kind of studying, so no problem.
Huh？ Then what kind of study do you mean？
Eh？ ▲高嶺＊＊▲. You're studying here again？
Yeah. Maybe someday, I can show you the results... I guess.
You can look forward to it.
I've got something to buy. What about you？
I also came to buy something.
Well, I guess I have to get going.
Umm. I was just thinking about you. So, when you suddenly showed up, I was really surprised.
Well, I guess I have to get going.
Ah, I knew, it was really you.
I caught a glimpse of you from faraway. Teehee. I'm glad I chased after you.
Well, I guess I have to get going.
